Description: Concave lip sherd of Attic pottery band-cup; interior: reserved at rim, glazed black below; exterior: lip glazed, trace of reserved zone below; inscription on exterior.
Bibliographic references: Bernand 1970 / Le Delta égyptien d'après les textes grecs, i: les confins libyques (pl. 22.2.11)
Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (GA.0515) (Phase 1)
